Standards-Version: 4.1.4

Package: ads-forwarder
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Tool to forward Beckhoff ADS connections
 A small tool that can scan for Beckhoff PLCs and forward connections
 through intermediate hosts. It also removes the need to know the
 AMS NetID of the target, or to explicitly set routes on it.
